Class User

java.lang.Object
pl.pjatk.MATLOG.domain.User
Direct Known Subclasses:
StudentUser, TutorUser
public abstract class User extends Object
Abstract class that represents User in application. User is meant to be extended by all concrete classes that represents a role.
